### Variables
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### Root endpoint - Welcome message
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get all posiciones (with pagination)
GET {{apiUrl}}?skip=0&limit=100
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get all posiciones (without pagination parameters)
GET {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get specific posicion by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new posicion
POST {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Gerente de Ventas",
  "descripcion": "Responsable de liderar el equipo de ventas",
  "salario_min": 50000.00,
  "salario_max": 75000.00
}

###

### Create another posicion
POST {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Desarrollador Senior",
  "descripcion": "Desarrollo de aplicaciones backend",
  "salario_min": 70000.00,
  "salario_max": 90000.00
}

###

### Create posicion with minimal data
POST {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Analista de Datos"
}

###

